正如普京所言，她的死亡对俄罗斯政府形象带来巨大的伤害。
这不是给克里姆林宫做任何的开脱。
不管普京是否亲自指挥，他创造的系统让这样的罪行得以发生。这样的系统是既无效又无用，都是一些无耻的演员参与的闹剧。
纳瓦尔尼的死是克林姆林宫想要的结果，让主子普京满意是走狗们的最终目标。
<s>In Putin's inner circle, loyalty is the only goal.
<s>Even if the poisoning fails, they won't face punishment.
<s>Because they do it for the president's benefit.
<s>Those who want to find proof of the poisoning might be disappointed.
<s>Still, the Kremlin is the mastermind.
<s>Western countries must clearly state that even if their economies are affected, they must take sanctions against Russia.
<s>Putin has created a system centered around himself.
<s>All responsibilities in Russia are attributed to him.
